How do I update this listing?




                                             Bares Capital Management is based out of Austin. Bares Capital Management is a large advisory firm with  26-100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $1,841,555,000 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $2,014,759,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 69.95%. Bares Capital Management's largest holding is Platform Specialty Products Corporation with shares held of 17,096,754.  Bares Capital Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 44 13Fs and  155 13D/G filings in our database for Bares Capital Management. 
                                           






