Bares Capital Management Inc 

Share with your friendsYour NameYour EmailRecipient EmailEnter a MessageI read this article and found it very interesting, thought it might be interesting for you. The article is called Bares Capital Management Inc and is was published by Octafinance.com at http://www.octafinance.com/hedge-funds/bares-capital-management-inc/.CaptchaSubmitBares Capital Management Inc is a Texas-based hedge fund that was founded by Brian Bares. It had more than $984.50 million assets under management in August, 2014. Taken from Bares Capital Management latest Adv, the fund reported to have 11 full and part-time employees. Among which 11 performing investment advisory and research functions. The hedge fund had more than 100 clients. Focusing his firm on bottom-up investments and small micro-cap companies, Brian Bares is the founder of Austin based Bares Capital Investments. Founded in 2000, Bares micro cap tactic grossed 53% in returns in 2010. As well as fund success, Bare has written “The Small Cap Advantage: How Top Endowments and Foundations Turn Small Stocks into Big Returns”. His educational background consists of a mathematics degree from the University of Nebraska.






